<%= render :partial => "layouts/main_banner"%>

<div class="blur">
<h1>Welcome</h1>
<h2>Our goal is to provide you with the top of the notch 
resorts around the world, just for you.</h2>
</div>

<div class="find_resort">
	<h3>FIND A RESORT</h3>
	<img src="/images/find_resort_icon.jpg" alt="find a resort" /><br/>
	<input type="text" name="location" value="Choose a Location" id="location_find"/><br/>
	<input type="text" name="city" value="Select a City" id="city"/><br/>
	<input type="submit" name="submit" value="find" id="submit" class="submit"/><br/>
</div>

<div class="boxes_down">

<div class="activities">
	<img src="/images/activities_image.jpg" alt="activities"/>
	<h3>ACTIVITIES</h3>
	<h4>Aspen Village</h4>
	<p>In winter, skiers and snow boarders enjoy Brundage Mountain from a base elevation of 6,000 feet.</p>
</div>

<div class="featured">
	<img src="/images/fetured_image.jpg" alt="featured resort"/>
	<h3>FEATURED</h3>
	<h4>7 Mile Beach</h4>
	<p>The Caribbean waters offer a full range of sports, including diving, snorkeling, windsurfing, and sailing</p>
</div>

<div class="join_club">
	<h3>JOIN THE CLUB</h3>
	<p class="no_margin">Subscribe to club and receive exclusive offers.</p>
	<input type="text" name="location" value="Choose a Location" id="location" class="input_colorado" /><br/>
	<input type="text" name="city" value="Select a City" id="city_join" class="input_colorado"/><br/>
	<input type="submit" name="submit" value="find" id="submit_join" class="submit_colorado"/><br/>
</div>

</div>